channel.title: Is there somesort of code out there to makr moparscape the atual thing?*read on*
channel.description:
I'm not looking for super modded up RS in a client, but all I want is the normal up to date RS or even RSC that has nobody on it, I don't care even if anyone can go on it, and the char can be edited (or just starts at lv. 126, 99 all stats0 and an auto save would be nice :\
i'm not sure if i'm asking a lot, please post back here or email whtsk8a-wot@hotmail.com if you have one you want to share with me

item.dc:creator: @breaking_the_bridge breaking the bridge
item.description:
@breaking_the_bridge wrote:

Bring up MoparScape 3.2 w\ Aryan and don’t type an Ip. Erase what it first given on the IP Bar when you load it. Just type a random username and pass and you will be satisfied

Read the rules here: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,3.0.html
Note:Edit your title so that is understandable in the language you speak.
